  QuestID: Quest8
  QuestName: Trial of the Island
  LevelRequirment: 0
  Instructions: Now we see what you're truly made of. Across this island stand ancient
    totems, each one a test left behind by those who came before us. Find one, face
    what it brings, and come back standing. That's all I ask.
  Deliver: You're still standing. Good. Most people avoid the totems, they'd rather
    not find out what they're capable of. You didn't hesitate. Remember that feeling.
